_sText: Another one of my maps just made... any problems please feel free to say so... Hope you enjoy Featuring: -2 Moving Boats ( 1 for Ct, 1 for T ) -Sexy water -Displacments -Destroyable Ammo Crates -Some other crap... Story Line: The Terroists have set up a small weapons & ammo dump on some small islands in the pacific. Ct: You have to destroy the ammo dumps and kill any remaining threats in the area. T: You have to patroll the surrounding islands and protect your ammo dumps. .NAV FILE NOW AVALIBLE: http://rapidshare.de/files/23243989/fy_pacific_islands.zip.html BIG THANKS TO JoeReaper FOR MAKING IT!
